javascript:(function(){function esc(s){return String(s).replace(/</g,'&lt;')}function dump(store){var h='';try{for(var i=0;i<store.length;i++){var k=store.key(i);h+='<div style="margin:3px 0;padding:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee"><b style="color:#06c;word-break:break-all">'+esc(k)+'</b><br><span style="word-break:break-all;color:#333">'+esc(store.getItem(k)).slice(0,300)+'</span></div>'}}catch(e){h='<i>blocked</i>'}return h||'<i>empty</i>'}var cookies=document.cookie?document.cookie.split(';').map(function(c){var p=c.trim().split('=');return'<div style="margin:3px 0;padding:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee"><b style="color:#c60;word-break:break-all">'+esc(p.shift())+'</b><br><span style="word-break:break-all;color:#333">'+esc(p.join('=')).slice(0,300)+'</span></div>'}).join(''):'<i>none</i>';var d=document.createElement('div');d.style.cssText='position:fixed;top:20px;right:20px;z-index:2147483647;background:#fff;color:#000;padding:14px;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.4);font:12px sans-serif;width:420px;max-width:92vw;max-height:82vh;overflow:auto';d.innerHTML='<b style="font-size:15px">Storage for '+esc(location.host)+'</b><br><br><b>🍪 Cookies</b>'+cookies+'<br><b>💾 localStorage ('+localStorage.length+')</b>'+dump(localStorage)+'<br><b>⏳ sessionStorage ('+sessionStorage.length+')</b>'+dump(sessionStorage);var clr=document.createElement('button');clr.textContent='clear all (this site)';clr.style.cssText='margin:10px 6px 0 0;color:#c00';clr.onclick=function(){if(!confirm('Clear all cookies, localStorage and sessionStorage for '+location.host+'?'))return;try{localStorage.clear()}catch(e){}try{sessionStorage.clear()}catch(e){}document.cookie.split(';').forEach(function(c){var n=c.split('=')[0].trim();document.cookie=n+'=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 GMT;path=/';document.cookie=n+'=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 GMT;path=/;domain=.'+location.host.replace(/^www\./,'')});d.remove();alert('Cleared. Reload the page to see the effect.')};var cl